===============
when it's possible:
===============

use Infinispan as a cache for users and maps
 - je potreba aby byl na openshiftu nejdrive umoznen domain mode https://openshift.redhat.com/community/content/jboss-as7-domain-mode
 - pouzit synchronizovanou distribuovanou Infinispan cache https://github.com/infinispan/infinispan-quickstart/tree/master/jboss-as7
replace openshift app to enable scalability https://openshift.redhat.com/community/developers/scaling

odstraneni kategorie z uzlu na serveru (ze vsech map) - jakmile to bude mozne provest pro vsechny naraz https://jira.mongodb.org/browse/SERVER-1243

